   The READNFO is to tell you that this has just one line of KORSUBS,   
   we ripped this near enough the same way as we ripped Killer Elite,   
   cropping up so there is just one row left, the row doesn't appear    
   all of the time. In our opinion if you crop anymore you end up       
   with too much picture loss and a squashed video. Just to add -       
   there's a nice little intro that we didn't bother to cut, it's       
   only about 20 seconds at the start of the movie. Ok, source was      
   pretty nice, had 3 rows of KORSUBS if i'm correct and had borders    
   on the top and bottom. So i dropped it in for filtering and          
   conversion, added in a few filters, cropped the black borders,       
   before then resizing and using the same crop script that we used     
   for Killer Elite. Turned out very nice, file size is a little        
   larger than normal, but all in all a sweet release. Took quite       
   a while to encode, remember it's free and Enjoy! 
